{"tid":2192271,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"昨晚個半小時內3男女墮樓亡 全部均沒有撿獲遺書及沒有可疑","createTime":"2020-09-07T04:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T07:50:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0799761fe339c20a495a2e1a3aa27eb0867cfa","tid":2192271,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"昨晚個半小時內，九龍及新界發生3宗墮樓案件，共有3人死亡。警方正調查3宗案件。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚約9時，一名51歲姓袁女子，被發現倒卧土瓜灣鵬程街一大廈外地上。救護員趕到發現她已奄奄一息，隨即將她送院搶救，可惜最終不治。警方未有撿獲遺書，初步相信她由大廈一單位墮下，事件沒有可疑。據知她有精神病及情緒病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n不足1小時後，沙田新田圍邨盛圍樓，一名23歲姓張女子，被發現倒卧大廈簷篷昏迷，她同樣被送院搶救後不治。警方沒有撿獲遺書，初步相信她由一樓層墮下，事件沒有可疑。據知她已婚，與丈夫疑因家事問題弄致不快。<br />\n<br />\n半小時後，一名70歲姓黃老翁，被發現倒卧荃灣大窩口邨富賢樓外地面，他由救護員送院搶救後不治。警方沒有撿獲遺書，初步相信他由單位墮下，事件沒有可疑。據知他有身體病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200907/EIPARW22IJGN7PSQSZ6OFDBCMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200907%2FEIPARW22IJGN7PSQSZ6OFDBCMA%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=97c1efe5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200907%2FEIPARW22IJGN7PSQSZ6OFDBCMA%2F&h=fc68240f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200907/EIPARW22IJGN7PSQSZ6OFDBCMA/</a>"},{"pid":"8df83408908ed07562cc87c404e9e7a6f3ea0ddd","tid":2192271,"uid":183844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:20:57.000Z","msg":"只望到我嗰刻有能力通知世界<br />\n不致橫死"},{"pid":"7d3ae0465478f339bb78b0a84da5920bfba8bf36","tid":2192271,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ba9a55af238cceafc